  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink278-kilavi">varaiyātu vantoḻukum talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the heroine said to the confidante, as the hero—who kept coming without marrying—was behind the hedge.                    
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink278">
<l>cilampiṉ vetirattuk kaṇviṭu kaḻaikkōl</l>
<l>kuraṅkiṉ vaṉpaṟaḻ pāynteṉa vilañci</l>
<l>mīṉeṟi tūṇṭili ṉivakku nāṭa</l>
<l>ṉuṟṟōr maṟavā nōytantu</l>
<l>kaṇṭōr taṇṭā nalaṅkoṇ ṭaṉaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>He of the land where the bamboo stalk,</l>
        <l>branching from a bamboo node</l>
        <l>on the mountain slope,</l>
        <l>springs forth like a hook thrown</l>
        <l>for fish in the pond,</l>
        <l>as the strong young of the monkey leaps—</l>
        <l rend="space indent">having given an unforgettable pain</l>
        <l rend="indent">to those who experienced [him];</l>
        <l rend="indent">has taken away her beauty,</l>
        <l rend="indent">which does not diminish</l>
        <l rend="indent">for those who look [at her].</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
